name: Digital Egg
description:
The game is about a Digital Monster who is trying to eat all internet data.
# There are only 5 levels if you reach the end, the game is over and starts from beginning.
# There is Z key for undo your movement.
# There are only Restart, Eating, Can't Move and Move Objects sounds in the game. 
# Don't mind the error, it's not effect the gameplay.
